privateJob.title: Muthoot Finance Recruitment 2021  Apply For Various JRE Posts
privateJob.body:
Name of the post:

  • Junior Relationship Executive

Description:

Muthoot Finance has issued a notification to fill the vacancies of various posts of Junior Relationship Executive. If you are finding jobs in location then feel free to apply online from The ProGrad .The candidates who are interested in the vacancies issued by Muthoot Finance can see the detailed information about key skills required, educational qualification, total vacancies, how to apply, roles, and responsibilities are given below. Muthoot Finance is dealing with banking and loan. If you are interested then read the details that are given below.

Total vacancies:

  • Various vacancies has released.

Selection Process:

  • Written Test
  • Group Discussion
  • Interview 

Roles and responsibility:

Canvasing and sourcing of New Customers to increase Gold loan Business, Revenue generation through Cross-Selling products & Interest Collection, Maintain good relationships with clients so that the business can maximize the value of those relationships. Customer Relationship and Follow-up, Maintenance of important registers and daily reports, Cash Management and Accounting


Application fee:

  • No information is given about the application fee.

Educational qualification:

The candidates who are interested to apply for the Muthoot Finance job must have the following qualification:

  • The candidates must have completed a degree from a recognized university to apply for the application Muthoot Finance Recruitment 2021

Key skills required :

The candidates who are interested to apply in these job openings must have the following key skills that are required to do this:

  • You must have knowledge of marketing and sales.

Payscale info. :

  • The Payscale information will be decided at the time of the interview.

The document needs to be carried:

The candidates who will be selected for the interview must carry the below-mentioned documents:

  • The first and foremost thing is your resume/CV which has your educational background and other related information.
  • You must have your Adhaar card for identity purposes.
  • You must have other identity proofs like a PAN card, voter id, or Passport to prove your citizenship.
  • At last, you should have photocopies of important educational certificates.

How to apply for Muthoot Finance Recruitment 2021?

Candidates who are eligible and interested to apply for Muthoot Finance Job then you should follow the below steps to apply:

  • Note: You can also apply by clicking the apply now button shown above to apply directly from here
  • First of all, read the Muthoot Finance Recruitment 2021 notification thoroughly at the official website @muthootfinance.com.
  • You should have an email id and a phone number for communication purposes.
  • Click on the apply now link for the post you want to apply for.
  • Fill in the required details and submit.
  • Pay the application fee asked for.
  • Finally submit and download the application form for future purposes.
